title: When (Specifically) does ranked season 2017 end?
body: I know ranked season ends on November 7th but what time? I'm halfway through placements and I want to know how long I have to grind. Does it finish at the start of November 7th or the end? Pls help {{sticker:slayer-jinx-catface}}

replies.body:
Following up on SephirothSG's post, here's the time in AEDT:

> 2017 SEASON ENDS:   NOVEMBER 07 4 AM AEDT

https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2017-ranked-season-ends-november-7

GL on the climb!

Hey there,

From what I can find the ranked season will end on November 8th at 07:00 GMT
